Thomy Bourdelle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomy_Bourdelle 0 Thomy Charles Bourdelle (20 April 1891 – 27 June 1972) was a French actor. Bourdelle was born in Paris and died in Toulon, Var, France.
